/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestContextManager::test_context_exit_calls_close -v`\n246: \n247: - [ ] **T5.10**: Test context manager exit on exception\n248:   - Purpose: Verify close() called even when exception raised\n249:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n250:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestContextManager::test_context_exit_on_exception -v`\n251: \n252: - [ ] **T5.11**: Test invoke delegation\n253:   - Purpose: Verify delegation to dp_client.invoke with session_id and payload\n254:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n255:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestInvoke::test_invoke_delegation -v`\n256: \n257: - [ ] **T5.12**: Test invoke without session raises ValueError\n258:   - Purpose: Verify ValueError when session_id is None\n259:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n260:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestInvoke::test_invoke_without_session -v`\n261: \n262: - [ ] **T5.13**: Test invoke timeout passed to data plane\n263:   - Purpose: Verify timeout argument passed through to dp_client.invoke\n264:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n265:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestInvoke::test_invoke_timeout_passthrough -v`\n266: \n267: - [ ] **T5.14**: Test close closes data plane\n268:   - Purpose: Verify dp_client.close() called\n269:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n270:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestClose::test_close_closes_data_plane -v`\n271: \n272: ### Phase 6: Integration Tests (ST-6)\n273: \n274: - [ ] **T6.1**: Test full session lifecycle with context manager\n275:   - Purpose: Verify bootstrap -> invoke -> close flow\n276:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py`\n277:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py::TestSessionLifecycle -v`\n278: \n279: - [ ] **T6.2**: Test invoke workflow with payload\n280:   - Purpose: Verify invoke returns response from agent\n281:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py`\n282:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py::TestInvokeWorkflow -v`\n283: \n284: - [ ] **T6.3**: Test session reuse across multiple invokes\n285:   - Purpose: Verify session_id reused across multiple invoke calls\n286:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py`\n287:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py::TestSessionReuseIntegration -v`\n288: \n289: - [ ] **T6.4**: Test error handling on bootstrap failure\n290:   - Purpose: Verify ValueError propagation on bootstrap failure\n291:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py`\n292:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py::TestBootstrapFailure -v`\n293: \n294: - [ ] **T6.5**: Test error handling on invoke failure\n295:   - Purpose: Verify HTTP error propagation on invoke failure\n296:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py`\n297:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py::TestInvokeFailure -v`\n298: \n299: ### Phase 7: Example Script (ST-7)\n300: \n301: - [ ] **T7.1**: Create `examples/agent_runtime_usage.py` example script\n302:   - Purpose: Provide usage example for AgentRuntimeClient\n303:   - File: `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_usage.py`\n304:   - Verification: `python sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_usage.py --help`\n305: \n306: ---\n307: \n308: ## Task Dependencies\n309: \n310: ```\n311: Phase 1 (AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient) ────────────────────────────────────────\n312: T1.1 (init) ──┬── T1.2 (SESSION_HEADER)\n313:               ├── T1.3 (base_url)\n314:               ├── T1.4 (connection pooling)\n315:               ├── T1.5 (bootstrap_session_id)\n316:                           └── T1.6 (missing header handling)\n317:               ├── T1.7 (invoke)\n318:                           ├── T1.8 (invoke headers)\n319:                           └── T1.9 (timeout override)\n320:               └── T1.10 (close)\n321: \n322: Phase 2 (AgentRuntimeClient) ────────────────────────────────────────\n323: T2.1 (init) ──┬── T2.2 (Router URL required)\n324:               ├── T2.3 (router URL resolution)\n325:               ├── T2.4 (session reuse)\n326:               ├── T2.5 (session bootstrap)\n327:               ├── T2.6 (_init_data_plane)\n328:               ├── T2.7 (__enter__)\n329:               ├── T2.8 (__exit__)\n330:               ├── T2.9 (invoke)\n331:                           └── T2.10 (session_id validation)\n332:               └── T2.11 (close)\n333: \n334: Phase 3 (Package Exports) ────────────────────────────────────────\n335: T1.1-T1.10 ───┬── T3.1 (clients/__init__.py)\n336: T2.1-T2.11 ───┬── T3.2 (agentcube/__init__.py)\n337: \n338: Phase 4-5 (Unit Tests) ────────────────────────────────────────\n339: T1.1-T1.10 ───┬── T4.1-T4.12 (data plane tests)\n340: T2.1-T2.11 ───┬── T5.1-T5.14 (client tests)\n341: \n342: Phase 6 (Integration Tests) ────────────────────────────────────────\n343: T4.1-T4.12 ───┬── T6.1-T6.5 (integration tests)\n344: T5.1-T5.14 ───┬── T6.1-T6.5 (integration tests)\n345: \n346: Phase 7 (Example) ────────────────────────────────────────\n347: T3.1-T3.2 ───┬── T7.1 (example script)\n348: ```\n349: \n350: ---\n351: \n352: ## Verification Commands\n353: \n354: | Task | Verification Command |\n355: |------|----------------------|\n356: | Phase 1 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py -v` |\n357: | Phase 2 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py -v` |\n358: | Phase 3 | `python -c \"from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient; from agentcube.clients import AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient; print('OK')\"` |\n359: | Phase 4 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py -v` |\n360: | Phase 5 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py -v` |\n361: | Phase 6 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py -v` |\n362: | Phase 7 | `python sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_usage.py --help` |\n363: | All Tests | `pytest sdk-python/tests/ -v -k \"agent_runtime\"` |\n364: \n365: ---\n366: \n367: ## Acceptance Criteria\n368: \n369: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeClient.__init__` with `agent_name`, `namespace`, `router_url`, `verbose`, `session_id`, `timeout`, `connect_timeout`\n370: - [ ] Router URL required: raises `ValueError` if missing via arg and env\n371: - [ ] Context manager: `__enter__` returns self, `__exit__` calls `close()`\n372: - [ ] Session reuse: skips `bootstrap_session_id` when `session_id` provided\n373: - [ ] `invoke`: validates `session_id` is not None before delegating\n374: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER` = `\"x-agentcube-session-id\"`\n375: - [ ] `bootstrap_session_id`: GET base_url, extract header, raise ValueError if missing\n376: - [ ] `invoke(session_id, payload, timeout)`: POST with headers `x-agentcube-session-id`, `Content-Type: application/json`\n377: - [ ] Timeout tuple: `(connect_timeout, timeout)` where timeout is passed arg or default\n378: - [ ] Base URL: `urljoin(router_url, f\"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/\")`\n379: - [ ] Connection pooling: `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n380: - [ ] Default timeouts: read `120s`, connect `5.0s`\n381: - [ ] No Authorization header on data plane (Router handles JWT)\n382: - [ ] All 12 data plane unit tests pass\n383: - [ ] All 14 client unit tests pass\n384: - [ ] All 5 integration tests pass\n385: - [ ] Example script runnable with `--help`\n386: \n387: ---\n388: \n389: ## File Changes Summary\n390: \n391: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n392: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n393: | `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | Create | ~100 | AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient implementation |\n394: | `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | Create | ~80 | AgentRuntimeClient implementation |\n395: | `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export AgentRuntimeClient |\n396: | `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient |\n397: | `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | Create | ~150 | Data plane client unit tests |\n398: | `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py` | Create | ~180 | Client unit tests |\n399: | `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_integration.py` | Create | ~80 | Integration tests |\n400: | `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_usage.py` | Create | ~40 | Usage example script |\n401: \n402: ---\n403: \n404: ## Implementation Notes\n405: \n406: ### Session Header Convention\n407: \n408: The session header is defined as a class constant:\n409: ```python\n410: class AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient:\n411:     SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"\n412: ```\n413: \n414: ### Base URL Construction\n415: \n416: ```python\n417: from urllib.parse import urljoin\n418: \n419: base_path = f\"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/\"\n420: self.base_url = urljoin(router_url, base_path)\n421: ```\n422: \n423: ### Bootstrap Session Flow\n424: \n425: ```python\n426: def bootstrap_session_id(self) -> str:\n427:     resp = self.session.get(self.base_url, timeout=(self.connect_timeout, self.timeout))\n428:     session_id = resp.headers.get(self.SESSION_HEADER)\n429:     if not session_id:\n430:         raise ValueError(\"Missing required response header: x-agentcube-session-id\")\n431:     return session_id\n432: ```\n433: \n434: ### Invoke Implementation\n435: \n436: ```python\n437: def invoke(self, session_id: str, payload: Dict[str, Any], timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> Response:\n438:     effective_timeout = timeout if timeout is not None else self.timeout\n439:     headers = {self.SESSION_HEADER: session_id, \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"}\n440:     resp = self.session.post(\n441:         self.base_url,\n442:         json=payload,\n443:         headers=headers,\n444:         timeout=(self.connect_timeout, effective_timeout)\n445:     )\n446:     return resp\n447: ```\n448: \n449: ### Router URL Resolution\n450: \n451: ```python\n452: router_url = router_url or os.environ.get(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n453: if not router_url:\n454:     raise ValueError(\"Router URL must be provided via argument or ROUTER_URL environment variable\")\n455: ```\n456: \n457: ### Context Manager Pattern\n458: \n459: ```python\n460: def __enter__(self):\n461:     return self\n462: \n463: def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):\n464:     self.close()\n465:     return False  # Don't suppress exceptions\n466: ```\n467: \n468: ### No Authorization on Data Plane\n469: \n470: The Router handles JWT authentication. The SDK does NOT set `Authorization` header on data plane requests—only the session header.\n471: \n472: ### Default Timeout Values\n473: \n474: | Timeout | Value | Purpose |\n475: |---------|-------|---------|\n476: | Read timeout | 120s | HTTP response read timeout |\n477: | Connect timeout | 5.0s | HTTP connection establishment |\n478: \n479: ---\n480: \n481: ## Implementation Timeline\n482: \n483: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n484: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n485: | Phase 1: DataPlaneClient | T1.1-T1.10 | Pending | 0% |\n486: | Phase 2: AgentRuntimeClient | T2.1-T2.11 | Pending | 0% |\n487: | Phase 3: Package Exports | T3.1-T3.2 | Pending | 0% |\n488: | Phase 4: DataPlane Tests | T4.1-T4.12 | Pending | 0% |\n489: | Phase 5: Client Tests | T5.1-T5.14 | Pending | 0% |\n490: | Phase 6: Integration Tests | T6.1-T6.5 | Pending | 0% |\n491: | Phase 7: Example | T7.1 | Pending | 0% |\n492: \n493: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/47 tasks)**\n494: \n495: ---\n496: \n497: ## References\n498: \n499: - Design: `changes/AR-028/design.md`\n500: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md`\n501: - Proposal: `changes/AR-028/proposal.md`\n502: - Python SDK Design: `python-sdk/design.md`\n503: - Python SDK Spec: `python-sdk/spec.md`\n504: - Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/`\n\n(End of file - total 504 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient |\n| Module | `sdk-python` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient Implementation (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.__init__` with router_url, namespace, agent_name, timeout, connect_timeout\n  - Purpose: Initialize HTTP client for Router data plane communication","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775881037195,"end":1775881037221}}}}
